title: Seif al-Islam el-Qaddafi, Son of Libyan Dictator, Is Killed
summary_full: Mr. el-Qaddafi, 53, a politician and a son of Col. Muammar el-Qaddafi, was killed after four men stormed his house, the lawyer said. No other details were released.
